# VibeCoder Freelance — Cursor Instructions

## Project Overview
VibeCoder — фриланс-маркетплейс AI-разработчиков и вайб-кодеров. React + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Appwrite 1.7.4 (self-hosted)
- Auth: Appwrite Account (shared across vibecoding.by projects)
- Deployment: Coolify on VPS 45.135.234.145

